cc:Work.dc:title: Track map of the route used for the Grand Prix of Detroit on Belle Isle
cc:Work.dc:description: Created in Inkscape using data from Google Earth. Because the vertical version of "Picnic Way" isn't text, I have hidden a duplicate text object by clipping it outside the image. If you need to edit that text, delete the existing object, unclip the original, and rebend that to fit (bend path effect).
